Package: acnexus
Version: 3.2-1
Depends: python3-light, python3-urllib, python3-email, python3-openssl, python3-xml
Section: utils
Architecture: all
Maintainer: oywq00008-cell
License: MIT
Description: AI-powered smart AC controller for Broadlink RM series.
 Supports 17 AC brands, dual weather sources (Baidu/QWeather),
 NMC/NHC dual storm tracking with intelligent wind-speed+distance tiered shutdown,
 multi-device management, schedule templates with multi-day groups,
 standalone temp rules, built-in hvac_ir/broadlink/schedule/pyaes (zero pip).
